				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ch%E1%BA%A5p-T%C3%ADn/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-b%C3%A0ng-bi/poem-43E9WYXE8ugsiEllasC4Aw">Đạo bàng bi - 道傍碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ch%E1%BA%A5p-T%C3%ADn/author-LcyqMNoBpNf6O7dZ2Ul1-Q">Triệu Chấp Tín</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-quan-san/poem-AacgT9F2TQnbuMwMeO8faw">Độ quan san - 度關山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/H%E1%BA%A1-ti%E1%BB%87p-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-Y9org3OKvblAJVYvS33jxg">Hạ tiệp kỳ 3 - 賀捷其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/M%E1%BA%A1i-th%C3%A1n-%C3%B4ng/poem-QxjelI7Fg2cw6NJQFsZzKA">Mại thán ông - 賣炭翁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-B%E1%BA%A1ch-M%C3%A3-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C6%B0u/poem-dW9R6UpAsABiUgZsSbvYjA">Tặng Bạch Mã vương Bưu - 贈白馬王彪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%87-l%C6%B0-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%